</p><p>Both of these calculations can be computed efficiently using the <a =
href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Square-and-multiply_algorithm" class=
=3D"mw-redirect" title=3D"Square-and-multiply algorithm">square-and-multipl=
y algorithm</a> for <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Modular_expone=
