<div class=3D"mw-heading mw-heading3"><h3 id=3D"Signing">Signing</h3><span =
class=3D"mw-editsection"><span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a =
href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=3DRSA_cryptosystem&amp;a=
ction=3Dedit&amp;section=3D9" title=3D"Edit section: Signing"><span>edit</s=
pan></a><span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></div>
<p>Suppose Alice wishes to send a signed message <span class=3D"texhtml mva=
r" style=3D"font-style:italic;">m</span> to Bob. She produces a <a href=3D"=
https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cryptographic_hash_function" title=3D"Cryptog=
raphic hash function">hash value</a> <span class=3D"texhtml"><i>h</i> =3D h=
ash(<i>m</i>)</span> of the message <span class=3D"texhtml mvar" style=3D"f=
ont-style:italic;">m</span>, raises it to the power of <span class=3D"texht=
ml mvar" style=3D"font-style:italic;">d</span> (modulo <span class=3D"texht=
ml mvar" style=3D"font-style:italic;">n</span>), and attaches <span class=
=3D"texhtml"><i>s</i> =3D <i>h</i><sup><i>d</i></sup> mod <i>n</i></span> a=
s a "signature" to the message.
</p>
<div class=3D"mw-heading mw-heading3"><h3 id=3D"Verifying">Verifying</h3><s=
pan class=3D"mw-editsection"><span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">[</span=
><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=3DRSA_cryptosystem&a=
mp;action=3Dedit&amp;section=3D10" title=3D"Edit section: Verifying"><span>=
edit</span></a><span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></div>
<p>When Bob receives the message <span class=3D"texhtml mvar" style=3D"font=
-style:italic;">m</span> and signature <span class=3D"texhtml mvar" style=
=3D"font-style:italic;">s</span>, he uses the same hash algorithm in conjun=
ction with Alice's public key to compute <span class=3D"texhtml"><i>h</i> =
=3D hash(<i>m</i>)</span>. He raises the signature <span class=3D"texhtml m=
var" style=3D"font-style:italic;">s</span> to the power of <span class=3D"t=
exhtml mvar" style=3D"font-style:italic;">e</span> (modulo <span class=3D"t=
exhtml mvar" style=3D"font-style:italic;">n</span>), and compares the resul=
ting hash value with the message's hash value: <span class=3D"mwe-math-elem=
ent mwe-math-element-block"><span class=3D"mwe-math-mathml-display mwe-math=
-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;"><math display=3D"block" xmlns=3D"htt=
p://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext=3D"{\displaystyle s^{e}\mathrel {\=
stackrel {?}{\equiv }} h{\pmod {n}}}">
  <semantics>
