ction-bracket">]</span></span></div>
<div class=3D"mw-heading mw-heading3"><h3 id=3D"Proof_using_Fermat's_little=
_theorem"><span id=3D"Proof_using_Fermat.27s_little_theorem"></span>Proof u=
sing Fermat's little theorem</h3><span class=3D"mw-editsection"><span class=
=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/w/i=
ndex.php?title=3DRSA_cryptosystem&amp;action=3Dedit&amp;section=3D12" title=
=3D"Edit section: Proof using Fermat's little theorem"><span>edit</span></a=
><span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></div>
<p>The proof of the correctness of RSA is based on <a href=3D"https://en.wi=
kipedia.org/wiki/Fermat%27s_little_theorem" title=3D"Fermat's little theore=
m">Fermat's little theorem</a>, stating that <span class=3D"texhtml"> <i>a<=
/i><sup><i>p</i> =E2=88=92 1</sup> =E2=89=A1 1 (mod <i>p</i>)</span> for an=
y integer <span class=3D"texhtml mvar" style=3D"font-style:italic;">a</span=
> and prime <span class=3D"texhtml mvar" style=3D"font-style:italic;">p</sp=
an>, not dividing <span class=3D"texhtml mvar" style=3D"font-style:italic;"=
>a</span>.<sup id=3D"cite_ref-41" class=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://en=
.wikipedia.org/wiki/RSA_cryptosystem#cite_note-41"><span class=3D"cite-brac=
ket">[</span>note 1<span class=3D"cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup>
</p><p>We want to show that
<span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-block"><span class=3D"mwe-=
math-mathml-display mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;"><math di=
splay=3D"block" xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext=3D"{\d=
isplaystyle (m^{e})^{d}\equiv m{\pmod {pq}}}">
  <semantics>
    <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
      <mstyle displaystyle=3D"true" scriptlevel=3D"0">
        <mo stretchy=3D"false">(</mo>
        <msup>
          <mi>m</mi>
          <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
            <mi>e</mi>
          </mrow>
        </msup>
        <msup>
          <mo stretchy=3D"false">)</mo>
          <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
            <mi>d</mi>
          </mrow>
        </msup>
        <mo>=E2=89=A1<!-- =E2=89=A1 --></mo>
        <mi>m</mi>
        <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
          <mspace width=3D"1em"></mspace>
          <mo stretchy=3D"false">(</mo>
          <mi>mod</mi>
