    <annotation encoding=3D"application/x-tex">{\displaystyle (m^{e})^{d}\e=
quiv m{\pmod {pq}}}</annotation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src=3D"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/rend=
er/svg/5ebb2828955ddd2510a60c32ea2ec12203752025" class=3D"mwe-math-fallback=
-image-display mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden=3D"true" style=3D"vertica=
l-align: -0.838ex; width:23.002ex; height:3.176ex;" alt=3D"{\displaystyle (=
m^{e})^{d}\equiv m{\pmod {pq}}}"></span>
for every integer <span class=3D"texhtml mvar" style=3D"font-style:italic;"=
>m</span> when <span class=3D"texhtml mvar" style=3D"font-style:italic;">p<=
/span> and <span class=3D"texhtml mvar" style=3D"font-style:italic;">q</spa=
n> are distinct prime numbers and <span class=3D"texhtml mvar" style=3D"fon=
t-style:italic;">e</span> and <span class=3D"texhtml mvar" style=3D"font-st=
yle:italic;">d</span> are positive integers satisfying <span class=3D"texht=
ml"><i>ed</i> =E2=89=A1 1 (mod <i>=CE=BB</i>(<i>pq</i>))</span>.
</p><p>Since <span class=3D"texhtml"><i>=CE=BB</i>(<i>pq</i>) =3D <a href=
=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Least_common_multiple" title=3D"Least com=
mon multiple">lcm</a>(<i>p</i> =E2=88=92 1, <i>q</i> =E2=88=92 1)</span> is=
, by construction, divisible by both <span class=3D"texhtml"><i>p</i> =E2=
=88=92 1</span> and <span class=3D"texhtml"><i>q</i> =E2=88=92 1</span>, we=
 can write
<span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-block"><span class=3D"mwe-=
math-mathml-display mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;"><math di=
splay=3D"block" xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext=3D"{\d=
isplaystyle ed-1=3Dh(p-1)=3Dk(q-1)}">
  <semantics>
    <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
      <mstyle displaystyle=3D"true" scriptlevel=3D"0">
        <mi>e</mi>
        <mi>d</mi>
        <mo>=E2=88=92<!-- =E2=88=92 --></mo>
        <mn>1</mn>
        <mo>=3D</mo>
        <mi>h</mi>
        <mo stretchy=3D"false">(</mo>
        <mi>p</mi>
        <mo>=E2=88=92<!-- =E2=88=92 --></mo>
        <mn>1</mn>
        <mo stretchy=3D"false">)</mo>
        <mo>=3D</mo>
        <mi>k</mi>
        <mo stretchy=3D"false">(</mo>
        <mi>q</mi>
        <mo>=E2=88=92<!-- =E2=88=92 --></mo>
        <mn>1</mn>
        <mo stretchy=3D"false">)</mo>
      </mstyle>
    </mrow>
    <annotation encoding=3D"application/x-tex">{\displaystyle ed-1=3Dh(p-1)=
=3Dk(q-1)}</annotation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src=3D"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/rend=
